[19:38] <sorear> What exactly *is* Callable?

[19:38] <pmichaud> it's the role for things that can be invoked.

[19:38] <pmichaud> the things that bind to a &-sigil

[19:38] <sorear> but &postcircumfix:<( )> isn't a method

